<https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-for/2020/3205> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:broader <https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-for/2020/32> ;
    skos:definition "This group covers human biochemistry or the chemistry of human living organisms and the human life process. It includes proteomics, metabolomics and metabolic medicine."@en ;
