    skos:scopeNote """a) Other material sciences are included in Groups 5104 Condensed matter physics, 3402 Inorganic chemistry, 3403 Macromolecular and materials chemistry, 4003 Biomedical engineering, 4016 Materials engineering and 4019 Resources engineering and extractive metallurgy.
