f) Biochemistry and proteomics associated with medical sciences is included in Group 3205 Medical biochemistry and metabolomics."""@en .

<https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-for/2020/3109> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:broader <https://linked.data.gov.au/def/anzsrc-for/2020/31> ;
    skos:definition "This group covers zoology."@en ;
